OOC: Tech problem prevented me from posting last night, again. Sorry.

::Hot Rod::

He listened to what IR said, and smiled. This was the atitude they
needed. A warriors mind set. A little Autobot spiret.

::Epyon::

He replyed to Alpha, "What is it?"

::KitKat2::

"A mistake led me to believe it was one of ours. Something was weird
though. No one stopped me it was like they knew me. Eventually I got out
and got back here. That on must have followed me."
